data.description: No sweepstake ballots here...this is your chance to clinch this HGTV model like home in the desirable Ocean Acres area of Barnegat, NJ! The meticulous upkeep of this 5 year home is evident in its cleanliness and well-maintained features. With attention to the custom detail at every turn, you can move in and start enjoying the lifestyle you've always dreamed of. The main level key features includes a cozy flex/bonus room, 1/2 bath, custom fitted window blinds, 9 ft ceilings, & tasteful vinyl plank flooring. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen featuring SS appliances, taintless granite countertops, custom made reclaimed wood shelving, & ample storage space for culinary enthusiasts. Convenience meets luxury with the laundry room conveniently located upstairs, making daily chores a breeze. The master suite accompanies three additional bedrooms and a full bath. The thoughtfully designed layout ensures that every inch of the home is utilized efficiently. One of the unique features of this home is the partially finished basement. Creative & fun, it provides a versatile space for a home office, gym, or entertainment area. The outdoor haven is perfect for entertaining guests or simply enjoying a peaceful evening under the stars.  Discover pure relaxation in the form of a MineCraft inspired custom designed patio with a posh pergola. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or sipping your morning coffee, this patio is sure to be your favorite spot. White vinyl fencing grants privacy while the fantastic fire pit sets the mood for singalongs and toasty s'mores. A 7 zone underground sprinkler system will keep your luscious sod looking its best. The owned solar panels yield a safety net for electric expenses year round. The builders home warranty is still in effect. This established home simply does not disappoint on Dylan Blvd. Don't miss the chance to make this stunning property your forever home.
